data.description: PROPERTY PRICED BELOW MARKET VALUE. List price is STARTING price. See attached EZ Offer addendums. Excellent investment opportunity! Currently well rented on AirBnb, seller happy to assist with transition. Well maintained duplex, with 2 beds, 2 baths on each side. Nice open floor plan with private screened lanai's to watch all the fruit trees in the yard! Dwarf varieties of Banana, Mango, Avocado, Coconut and Lemon trees, so they won't consume the yard. Close to shopping and restaurants! Furnishings are negotiable! Check out the virtual walkthrough
